snippet.title: Valheim: Mistlands Gameplay Trailer [CONTAINS SPOILERS]
snippet.description:
As the mist stirs, long forgotten secrets are unveiled... Will you be brave and resilient enough to discover them?

This is a gameplay trailer, and is obviously not spoiler free!
The Mistlands update is available NOW for Public Testing. Read more about how to join, as well as read the full patch notes, on our website: https://valheim.com/news/mistlands-public-test

Get Valheim with PC Game Pass, or buy it now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/892970/Valheim/

Valheim is made by developer Iron Gate, published by Coffee Stain Publishing.
